						The Saville Inquiry into Bloody Sunday
					</a>
				</h3>
				<a class="ddyy" href="/web/20120131204213/http://www.bbc.co.uk/history/events/saville_inquiry_into_bloody_sunday">
					<span>
						<b>03 April</b> 1998 -<br /> <b>15 June</b> 2010					</span>
				</a>
			</li>

